{"tid":221074,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[LOL]大家身邊有冇朋友係\"NG達人\"？","createTime":"2017-04-28T12:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T14:06:45.000Z","uid":45185,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4140d687f36f5ebdd6cea16a8713fed03ddd7c","tid":221074,"uid":45185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:22:59.000Z","msg":"&quot;NG達人&quot;特徵有:<br />\n<br />\n1.淨係打NG扮清泉，甚少/冇打積分。<br />\n<br />\n2.經常拎NG戰績打飛機/周圍send想人讚<br />\n<br />\n3.成日見到牌位高既人都懶勁加衝出嚟柒;覺得自己觀念技術都比佢好。<br />\n<br />\n4.有自己一套獨特既打法，不過係廢既。永遠唔同意主流打法，例如出裝順序、升技能次序，<a href=\"http://啫係op.gg/kr果啲數據。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%95%AB%E4%BF%82op.gg%2Fkr%E6%9E%9C%E5%95%B2%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E3%80%82&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=60a5e54f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">啫係op.gg/kr果啲數據。</a><br />\n<br />\n5.對NG有一種執著，就算隊友全部正正常常，對面隊真係比較勁輸既比數差距唔大，明明一場好玩既遊戲都會瀨人廢或者嘴炮發老脾，惱羞成怒。<br />\n<br />\n6.口頭禪有&quot;自問勁過___牌位，不過我唔打積分咋嘛&quot;<br />\n<br />\n原因 i)懶得打 ii)冇時間打 iii)跌落地拿返渣沙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好啦我認我唔敢直接屌柒條垃圾</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e77e6fa1450e66b71e8fa4f2a5735623fbe969","tid":221074,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8abbc07c43305b25b177f0f0b8190a3ff4675c4","tid":221074,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa891c17c956e5a545bc9a2f03fc4b1d891ef873","tid":221074,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"唔係針對中小學雞，真係聽聞過有啲成廿鳩幾歲既人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf5633833496db298a58b65faeea1a5ce42